name: Korra - Legend of Korra
description:
I was just looking more closely and I think her eyes are supposed be slightly green. Whoops... 😭

Made two versions.

V1 - Has fairly rigid clothes. If you prompt hard enough, you can change them. Her collar is hard to take off, however.

V2 - Clothes are very flexible. It's inclined to make her naked in fact... Face is not quite as good, imo.

If you like either one, leave a positive review, if you don't mind... I'll feel better about myself.

modelVersions.name: V1 - More Accurate Clothes
modelVersions.description: This version can create clothes that are pretty close to what she wears in the show from the waist up. Personally, I like this version more.
